<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Expense Tracker/Dashboard</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="login.css">
        <style>
           
        /* Style for placeholder text */
        input::placeholder {
            font-size: 18px; /* Adjust the font size */
            color: #aaa; /* Placeholder color */
            opacity: 1; /* Ensure full opacity */
        }

        .form-control {
            font-size: 20px; /* Font size for the input field */
            padding: 10px; /* Add padding for comfort */
        }

        .form-content {
            font-size: 20px; /* Font size for the password field */
            padding: 10px; /* Add padding for comfort */
        }
    
        </style>

    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <nav>
                <div class="logo"><h1>Dashboard</h1></div>
                <div class="links">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a class="active" href="#" style="font-size: 25px;"> Home</a></li>
                        <li><a class href="#" style="font-size: 23px;">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" style="font-size: 23px;">Contacts</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </nav>
            <div class="home-content">
                <div class="left-container">
                    <div class="home-container">
                        <h1 class="heading ">My Expense Tracker.</h1>
                        <div class="paragraphs">
                        <P1 class="p1">Take control of your daily spending and gain insight into your financial habits. 
                            Does your spending truly align with your income? You might have an idea, but let’s dig deeper.
                       </P1><br/><br/>

                       <p2 class="p2">  Have you ever wondered why the wealthy stay wealthy while others struggle? 
                        The key lies in mastering cash flow—understanding both income and expenses.  </p2><br/><br/>

                        <p3 class="p3"> Now’s your chance to track your spending and make more informed financial decisions.
                            Ready to take control? Let’s begin the journey to better financial health!</p3>

                       
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <!-- Loging form -->
                <div class="card shadow reg-card">
                    
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <form action="/auth/login" method="post">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="email" class="fw-bold" style="font-size: 25px;">Email Address</label>

                                <input 
                                type="text" 
                                class="form-control"
                                id="Email Address" 
                                placeholder="Enter your Email Address"
                                 required name="email"
                                 />
                            </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                 <label for="password" class="fw-bold" style="font-size: 25px;">Password</label>
                                <input 
                                type="password" 
                                class="form-content"
                                id="password" 
                                placeholder="Enter your password" 
                                required name="Password"/>
                        
                             </div>
                             <div class="remember-me">
                                <input type="checkbox" style="transform: scale(1.9); margin: 20px;">
                                <span style="color: #0e0d0d">I accept Terms of Service</span>
                            </div>
                            
                             <button type="submit" class="btn" style="font-size: 20px;">Login</button>

                             <div class="register">
                             <span>Don't have an account?</span>
                             <a href="/register" class="btn-register" style="font-size: 20px; text-decoration: none;">Register here</a>
                              </div>


                            <div class="privacy">
                                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                            </div>
                    
                            
                        </div>
                    
                           
                            
                        
                            
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    

                </div>

            
                
                
        </header>
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Expense Tracker. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </footer>
        <script src="./login-script.js"></script>
        
    </body>
</html>